The paper discusses a new class of functions and their computational complexity, which suggests that it could belong to the categories of computational complexity (cs.CC), cryptography and security (cs.CR), information theory (cs.IT), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and discrete mathematics (cs.DM).
